DHCPv6 and DHCPv6 options - per [RFC3315]

(last updated 2007-04-26)

- Message types
- Option codes
- Status codes
- DUID

For the Civic Address Types Registry [RFC4776], please see:
http://www.iana.org/assignments/civic-address-types-registry

DHCP Message types

Value     Description                    Reference
-----     ----------------------         ---------
    1     SOLICIT                        [RFC3315]
    2     ADVERTISE                      [RFC3315]
    3     REQUEST                        [RFC3315]
    4     CONFIRM                        [RFC3315]
    5     RENEW                          [RFC3315]
    6     REBIND                         [RFC3315]
    7     REPLY                          [RFC3315]
    8     RELEASE                        [RFC3315] 
    9     DECLINE                        [RFC3315]
   10     RECONFIGURE                    [RFC3315]
   11     INFORMATION-REQUEST            [RFC3315]
   12     RELAY-FORW                     [RFC3315]
   13     RELAY-REPL                     [RFC3315]

