Status Codes

Code  Name                Reference
----  ------------        ---------
   0  Success             [RFC3315]
   1  UnspecFail          [RFC3315]
   2  NoAddrsAvail        [RFC3315]
   3  NoBinding           [RFC3315]
   4  NotOnLink           [RFC3315]
   5  UseMulticast        [RFC3315] 
   6  NoPrefixAvail       [RFC3633]                

