   3   DUID-LL                 [RFC3315]

References
----------
[RFC3315]  R. Droms (ed.), J. Bound, B. Volz, T. Lemon, C. Perkins, 
           and M. Carney, "Dynamic Host Configuration Protocol for 
           IPv6 (DHCPv6)", RFC 3315, July 2003.

[RFC3319]  H. Schulzrinne and B. Volz, "DHCPv6 Options for SIP Servers"
           RFC 3319, July 2003.

[RFC3646]  R. Droms, Ed., "DNS Configuration options for DHCPv6", RFC 3646,
           December 2003.

[RFC3633]  O. Troan and R. Droms, "IPv6 Prefix Options for DHCPv6", RFC 3633,
           December 2003.

[RFC3898]  V. Kalusivalingam, "NIS Configuration Options for DHCPv6", RFC 3898,
           October 2004.

[RFC4075]  V. Kalusivalingam, "Simple Network Time Protocol Configuration Option 
           for DHCPv6", RFC 4075, May 2005.

[RFC4280]  K. Chowdhury, P. Yegani and L. Madour, "DHCP Options for Broadcast 
           and Multicast Control Servers", RFC 4280, November 2005.

[RFC4242]  S. Venaas, T. Chown, and B. Volz, "Information Refresh Time Option for 
           DHCPv6", RFC 4242, November 2005.

[RFC4776]  H. Schulzrinne, "Dynamic Host Configuration Protocol (DHCPv4 and DHCPv6) 
           Option for Civic Addresses Configuration Information", RFC 4776, November 2006.

[RFC4649]  B. Volz, "DHCPv6 Relay Agent Remote ID Option", RFC 4649, August 2006.

[RFC4580]  B. Volz, "DHCPv6 Relay Agent Subscriber-ID Option", RFC 4580, June 2006.
 
[RFC4704]  B. Volz, "The DHCPv6 Client FQDN Option", RFC 4704, October 2006.

[RFC-ietf-dhc-paa-option-05.txt]
           L. Morand, A. Yegin, S. Kumar, S. Madanapalli, "DHCP options for PANA 
           Authentication Agents", RFC XXXX, Month, Year.

[RFC4833]  E. Lear, P. Eggert, "A Timezone Option for DHCP", RFC 4833,
		    April 2007.


